  "description": "A wide-angle shot captures the San Francisco skyline under a cloudy, overcast sky. The iconic Golden Gate Bridge dominates the background, stretching across the bay. A collection of modern skyscrapers and high-rise buildings forms a dense urban landscape on the left, contrasting with the more residential, hilly areas visible on the right side of the frame. The bay's water is choppy and gray, reflecting the cloudy sky. Several boats are scattered throughout the bay. The scene depicts a harmonious blend of natural beauty and urban development.",
